MID_支援_エルフィ_ハロルド_Ｃ: $t1$Wmエルフィ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsハロルド|$WaElfie, my friend, do you have a moment?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaWhat's the matter, Harold?\nDid something happen to Lady Elise?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaNo, that's not it.\nI must speak to you about something.$k$pYou and I both serve Lady Elise.$k$pJust like you, I wish to protect her\nfrom the bottom of my heart.$k$pHowever... I have noticed something\nrecently. That you and I are different.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa...Different?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaYes.$k$pYou feelings towards protecting\nLady Elise are outstanding.$k$pYou and I are both people who believe\nthat we should act for the people.$k$pBut when it comes to Lady Elise, you...\nsuddenly exhibit unearthly powers.$k$p$Eキメ,|What is your secret to it?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E苦,|Umm...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,|...The battles are getting\nmore intense by the day.$k$pThe importance of protecting Lady\nElise has grown much more dire.$k$pIf there is a method to your ways, I would\nlike to receive some advice from you.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E怒,|…………$k$p...Like you, the relationship between Lady\nElise and I is that of master and servant.$k$pHowever, before that, Lady Elise\nand I are childhood friends.$k$pI think that explains the difference between\nmy relationship with her compared to yours.$k$pAnd so... that's why I don't\nhave any advice for you.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|…………$k$pIs... is that so...$k
MID_支援_エルフィ_ハロルド_Ｂ: $t1$Wmエルフィ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsエルフィ|$WaHarold.\nAbout the talk we had last time...$k$pThere's one more difference\nbetween the two of us...$k$pIt's that I'm not as fickle as you...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|...Fickle?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaWhen people are in trouble, you do\neverything in your power to help them...$k$pYou go out of your way to save people\nwho have no relation to Lady Elise.$k$pBut I am different...$k$p$Eキメ,|Lady Elise is my foundation.\nNo matter what happens, I will defend her.$k$pFurthermore, I will rescue those\nwho are connected to her.$k$pAlways thinking about Lady Elise,\nonly doing things for Lady Elise...$k$pEating a lot more for Lady Elise...\nUsing my power for the sake of Lady Elise...$k$p$E通常,|That might be the difference between us.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常2,|I... I see...$k$p…………$k$pLady Elise is also very important to me.\nHowever...$k$p$Eキメ,|When I hear lost children, I search\ndesperately for their parents.$k$pWhen I see the elderly with legs tired from\nwalking, my back serves as their legs.$k$pWhen I hear a child cry, I must\ncry with them until they smile.$k$pAnd when I see a fight, I must intervene\nand turn both fists into a handshake.$k$pThis is how I am...$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E通常,|…………$k$pWell...\nYou're fine as you are, aren't you?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|Thank you, Elfie.\nThanks to you, I truly understand myself.$k$pThis conversation today shall be a\npoint of reference for the future.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E笑,|Is that so...$k
MID_支援_エルフィ_ハロルド_Ａ: $t1$Wmエルフィ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsエルフィ|$WaHarold...\nI wanted to talk to you about something...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$WaWhat is it?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E怒,|What's happened to you?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|"What's happened"?\nWhat do you mean?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaIn our recent battles, you've been\nlacking that gleam of ambition.$k$pI can tell your movements are lackluster\ncompared to how you normally are.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|…………$k$pI see...$k$pWell, I did a bit of introspection.$k$pI stopped my normal schedule of\nrescuing people, slept earlier at night,$k$pcompletely stopped my habit\nof surveying the area...$k$pInstead, I used that time for Lady Elise,\njust like you.$k$pAlways thinking about Lady Elise,\nonly doing things for Lady Elise...$k$pEating a lot for Lady Elise,\nusing my powers for Lady Elise...$k$pI did my best to fill in the\ngap that separated us, but...$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E苦,|That's strange, Harold...$k$pI didn't say you were wrong.$k$pIn fact, I respect your actions\nfor overflowing with justice.$k$pI cannot serve thousands of\npeople in the name of justice...$k$pAnd that's what's good about you,\nyour source of energy.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|I see...$k$pAlthough I thought it was for the best,\ndeciding to change myself was a mistake.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes...$k$pI have my way of doing things,\nand you have yours...$k$pNeither way is better than the other,\nneither way is wrong.$k$pThat's why you should go about\nit the way that you want...$k$p$E笑,|...Because those actions will,\nin return, be for Lady Elise.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,|I understand.\nThank you for your wonderful advice.$k$pVery well, I will do things my own way...\nIn the name of justice, my own path...$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaYes. You are everyone's\nally of justice, Harold...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,|...Elfie, my friend!\nThank you.$k$pFrom now on, let us together\ndo our best for Lady Elise.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes, let's.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|...By the way Elfie, are you\ninterested in the path of justice?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$