MID_支援_エルフィ_ハロルド_Ｓ: $t1$Wmエルフィ|7$Wmハロルド|3$w0|$Wsエルフィ|$WaHarold... What did you want,\ncalling me out to this place?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|Ah, sorry about that.$k$pI wanted to tell you something important,\nbut I decided against it,$k$psince something I needed\nhasn't been delivered.$k$pFor goodness' sake,\nwhat on earth is happening...$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaCould it be this box...?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,|Ehhh!?\nY-yes, it is indeed!$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaFor some reason, this got\ndelivered to my place...$k$pAnd I had a look inside the box just\nto check, and there was a ring.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,|Y-y-you looked inside the box!?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E苦,|I did. Sorry... but it's definitely\nyours, isn't it Harold?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,汗|Guh!! That stupid jeweller!\nI told them to send it to me...$k$pWhy, out of all places, did\nthey send it to Elfie...!?$k$pHow about we forget about this.$k$pSince the ring has been delivered to her,\nthere's no turning back now...$k$p$Eキメ,|You can do it, right Harold?$k$pNo, it's not about whether I can or\ncan't do it... I'm going to do it...$k$pI must do it!$k$pIf I don't do it right now, I would\nbe opposing the way of justice!$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E怒,汗|...Harold?$k$pWhat are you doing muttering to yourself...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa…………$k$p...Ahem. Let me begin, Elfie.$k$p$Eキメ,照|I had a purpose for calling you here.\nI would like you to accept that ring.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E通常,|But I already received it...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,照|N-no, well you indeed have, but...\nI don't mean accept it in that way...$k$pI want you to accept it\nas proof of marriage.$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E苦,照|!? M-marriage!?\nMe... to you?$k$pBut... but... I...$k$p$E苦,|...don't really understand, why marriage...$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E苦,照|Eh?$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I think only of Lady Elise...\nI do things for the sake of Lady Elise...$k$pEating a lot for Lady Elise...\nUsing my powers for Lady Elise...$k$p$E通常,|That is all I am.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E通常,|Elfie...$k$pThat's fine, you don't have to worry.\nYou are fine as you are.$k$p$E通常,照|Only that I will be in\nyour life a little more...$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$WaI see...$k$p$E通常,照|If that's the case... I don't mind...\nI accept with pleasure.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E怒,照|R-really!?\nThat was a bit...anticlimatic, though...$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E怒,照|...Well if you think about it,\nyou and I are partners...$k$pWe were always together until now, so\nyou've already accepted my way of thinking.$k$p$E通常,照|That's why I have no reason to object.\nIn fact, you've only encouraged me more.$k$pFor a person like you to\nalways be by my side...$k$p$E笑,照|From now on, as a life partner...\nPlease take care of me, Harold.$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$E笑,照|Elfie...!$k$pI'm glad to hear those words.\nPlease take care of me as well.$k$pNow and hereafter,\nwe will be the best partners!$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E通常,照|Yes.$k$pThe one that is most suited\nto be beside me is you...$k$pThank you... Harold.\nI accept this ring wholeheartedly.$k$pAfter I put it on... shall we\ngo show Lady Elise...?$k\n$Wsハロルド|$Wa$Eキメ,照|A fine idea! I'm sure Lady Elise will give\nus her blessings to our new beginnings!$k\n$Wsエルフィ|$Wa$E笑,照|Ehehe, I'm sure she will...$k
